/>\n睇過傲慢與偏見既勞工。<br />\n<br />\n加油，<br />\n如果真係勁唔開心，<br />\n就尋求外界協助。<br />\n<br />\n當年我爆煲拎刀斬我老豆老母，<br />\n我都係自己打９９９尋求協助，<br />\n<br />\n我慶幸自己無斬落佢地條頸度，<br />\n如果唔係就真係鑄成無可挽救既大錯。<br />\n<br />\n加油，<br />\n我都係康復途中。<br />\n<br />\n我好得返，<br />\n你都一定得。<br />\n而且我相信你重後生，<br />\n重有大把時間可以比你改進精進自己，<br />\n唔好咁灰心。<br />\n<br />\n雨過總會天晴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T20:32:25.000Z","msg":"多謝你阿巴打  打咁長<br />\n其實大家都辛苦  只係冇講出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T20:40:02.000Z","msg":"訓啦，聽日其實重要開工<br />\n<br />\n唔好係度怨天怨地啦，<br />\n<br />\n唔鍾意條仔既就飛左條仆街仔佢啦。<br />\n不過，無一條友會想自己既另一半成日都負能量。<br />\n<br />\n我以前負能量到我中文同英文老師都主動刪除左我ＦＡＣＥＢＯＯＫ。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家我ＦＡＣＥＢＯＯＫ得返２０幾條友<br />\n我挑佢地老味，<br />\n佢地唔想接受我既負能量，<br />\n我就主動自己ＤＥＬＥＴＥ晒啲人囉，<br />\n<br />\n反正根本真正關心你既人係好撚少。<br />\n<br />\n世界上最愛你既，９９％係你父母。<br />\n<br />\n我講野真係唔撚叻，<br />\n所以而家都係單身狗，<br />\n加油啦，<br />\n<br />\n自棄者，扶不起；自強者，打不倒。<br />\n<br />\n我唔得閒同你顛。。。因為我真係夠鐘訓教。<br />\n<br />\n好好愛自己，<br />\n連自己都唔珍惜自己，<br />\n又有邊個會珍惜你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（呢句野唔係只係同你講，重有我自己同自己講）<br />\n<br />\n大家都辛苦大家都有壓力，<br />\n最緊要搵到岩你自己既方法爆出黎但又唔好傷害人地。<br />\n<br />\n大大力對住山邊大叫一句屌佢老母，<br />\n可能都抒發到自己好多既情緒！<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109b34de24e48abd076800a17e50a0032e65b9e5","tid":1153681,"uid":139919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T21:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b911abf4a9e73c6e5918b4fadc2d8c86bdc5c55","tid":1153681,"uid":242301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}